for lang in $linguas; do \
  dir=/var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/image//usr/share/locale/$lang/LC_MESSAGES; \
  /bin/sh /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/gtk/install-sh -d $dir; \
  if test -r $lang.gmo; then \
    /usr/lib/portage/python3.6/ebuild-helpers/xattr/install -c -m 644 $lang.gmo $dir/ghb.mo; \
    echo "installing $lang.gmo as $dir/ghb.mo"; \
  else \
    /usr/lib/portage/python3.6/ebuild-helpers/xattr/install -c -m 644 /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/build/../gtk/po/$lang.gmo $dir/ghb.mo; \
    echo "installing /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/build/../gtk/po/$lang.gmo as" \
	 "$dir/ghb.mo"; \
  fi; \
  if test -r $lang.gmo.m; then \
    /usr/lib/portage/python3.6/ebuild-helpers/xattr/install -c -m 644 $lang.gmo.m $dir/ghb.mo.m; \
    echo "installing $lang.gmo.m as $dir/ghb.mo.m"; \
  else \
    if test -r /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/build/../gtk/po/$lang.gmo.m ; then \
      /usr/lib/portage/python3.6/ebuild-helpers/xattr/install -c -m 644 /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/build/../gtk/po/$lang.gmo.m \
	$dir/ghb.mo.m; \
      echo "installing /var/tmp/portage/media-video/handbrake-1.2.2-r2/work/HandBrake-1.2.2/build/../gtk/po/$lang.gmo.m as" \
	   "$dir/ghb.mo.m"; \

      true; \
    fi; \
  fi; \
